Hello! Thank you for contacting Aquidneck Yacht Brokers. My name is Scott Watson. May I ask who I'm speaking with today?

Hi Scott, this is Danielle Allen. Thanks for taking my call!

It's a pleasure to speak with you, Danielle. How can I assist you today?

I'm experiencing some equipment malfunction on my boat and I need a bit of guidance.

I'm sorry to hear that, Danielle. Could you let me know specifically what equipment is malfunctioning?

It's the navigation system that's acting up. It won't display correctly.

Thank you for the information. Can I please have the model number of your navigation system?

Sure, the model number is N-A-V one two zero zero.

Got it, and just for security purposes, could you confirm the last four digits of the hull identification number?

Of course, it's five six seven eight.

Thank you, Danielle. I'll look into this issue and get back to you shortly with a solution.

I appreciate your help, Scott. Thank you so much for your time.

You're welcome, Danielle. Thank you for calling Aquidneck Yacht Brokers. Have a great day!
